            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EWhat%20would%20we%20do%20without%20the%20%22handfuls%20of%20purpose%2C%22%20which%20the%20Lord%20of%20the%20harvest%20intentionally%20leaves%20out%20for%20us%3F%20If%20Boaz%20had%20not%20instructed%20his%20men%20to%20drop%20some%20daily%20provision%20for%20Ruth%2C%20she%20and%20Naomi%20would%20have%20perished.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhen%20our%20lives%20seem%20insignificant%20and%20full%20of%20drudgery%20and%20routine%2C%20we%20must%20remember%20that%20God%20has%20things%20working%20for%20us%20which%20we%20never%20imagined.%20Just%20when%20Ruth's%20back%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20breaking%20and%20her%20bread%20bag%20was%20empty%2C%20she%20found%20a%20generous%20handful%20of%20purpose.%20Just%20when%20we%20think%20God%20has%20forgotten%20about%20us%2C%20He%20drops%20us%20a%20handful%20of%20purpose.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJoseph%20was%20languishing%20in%20an%20Egyptian%20prison.%20It%20seemed%20as%20though%20God%20had%20forgotten%20him%20and%20his%20life%20was%20destined%20to%20drudgery%20and%20misery.%20Then%20suddenly%2C%20out%20of%20nowhere%2C%20God%20dropped%20Joseph%20a%20handful%20of%20purpose%20in%20the%20dream%20of%20Pharaoh%20(Psalm%20105%3A19).%20%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EGod%20will%20drop%20little%20signs%20here%20and%20there%20to%20remind%20you%20of%20His%20sovereign%20direction%20and%20destiny%20for%20your%20life.%20Even%20in%20your%20struggles%2C%20all%20things%20are%20working%20together%20for%20good%20because%20you%20are%20called%20according%20to%20His%20purpose%20(Romans%208%3A28).%20Never%20forget%3A%20%22Boaz%22%20has%20his%20eyes%20upon%20you!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
